address: The P2PKH address corresponding to the private key you want returned. Must be an address corresponding to a private key in this wallet.
field1: put in helpful info for field1
help:
The dumpprivkey RPC returns the wallet-import-format (WIP) private key corresponding to an address. (But does not remove it from the wallet). 

 Parameter #1—the address corresponding to the private key to get. 

 Result—the private key.
